item.title: About
item.description: I’m Carter, and this is my blog. Some of the posts here will be about technical things, and others will be about completely non-technical things that are also (hopefully) interesting (to somebody besides me). Here’s are some facts about me: I have a thing for lists. No, seriously. They’re like, hands down my favorite way to present information. I’m originally from Spokane but I’m currently living in San Francisco. I graduated from Dartmouth’s CS program in 2017, and now I’m a software developer on Khan Academy’s engineering team!
